Perry et al., Respondents, v. Boomhower, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J„ and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument denied, with $10 costs. Eor decision on appeal, see 17 N. Y. Supp. 890.
